    <item>
      <title>交易员预计中国债券收益率将跌至 1.5%，因市场普遍看好股市上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-10/traders-see-china-yield-fall-to-1-5-on-everything-rally-hope</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国明年将转向宽松的货币政策，这引发了人们看涨的押注，即中国主权债务收益率将从历史低点进一步下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-10/traders-see-china-yield-fall-to-1-5-on-everything-rally-hope</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 10 Dec 2024 01:49:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度任命马洛特拉为央行行长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-12-10/india-names-malhotra-to-lead-central-bank-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度任命职业官僚桑杰·马洛特拉为该国央行新行长，结束了数周以来关于谁将掌管这个世界增长最快的主要经济体货币政策的猜测。这位拥有普林斯顿大学公共政策硕士学位的新行长将从 12 月 11 日起执掌印度储备银行，任期三年。彭博社的 Avril Hong 在《彭博：亚洲贸易》中报道了此事。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-12-10/india-names-malhotra-to-lead-central-bank-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 10 Dec 2024 01:46:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>高层领导暗示将推出更大胆刺激措施 中国股市上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-10/chinese-stocks-rally-after-top-leaders-signal-bolder-stimulus</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在中国高层领导人做出多年来最强有力的恢复经济增长的承诺后，中国股市周二上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-10/chinese-stocks-rally-after-top-leaders-signal-bolder-stimulus</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 10 Dec 2024 01:32:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>惠誉评级称韩国风险上升，但不会持续太久</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-12-10/fitch-ratings-says-korea-risks-elevated-but-short-lived-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[惠誉评级亚太区主权评级总监 Jeremy Zook 表示，韩国总统迅速撤销戒严令以及随后的社会动荡将在短期内使政治风险居高不下，但由于该国经历过政治动荡，经验表明其主权信用状况并未受到重大损害。他在“彭博社：亚洲贸易”节目中与 Shery Ahn 和 Haidi Stroud-Watts 进行了交谈。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-12-10/fitch-ratings-says-korea-risks-elevated-but-short-lived-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 10 Dec 2024 01:30:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>阿波罗首席执行官以现金购买价值 4.31 亿美元的股份，最终可能会出售</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-10/apollo-ceo-taps-cash-on-431-million-stake-may-end-up-selling</link>
      <description><![CDATA[阿波罗全球管理公司 (Apollo Global Management Inc.) 首席执行官马克·罗文 (Marc Rowan) 投入了价值 4.31 亿美元的公司股票，并可能最终将其出售，因为他希望获得与该公司相关的部分财富。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-10/apollo-ceo-taps-cash-on-431-million-stake-may-end-up-selling</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 10 Dec 2024 00:55:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>韩国股市在因政治危机损失 1000 亿美元后上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-10/korean-stocks-gain-after-losing-100-billion-to-political-crisis</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国股市周二上涨，寻求自上周短暂戒严令导致该国陷入政治动荡以来的首次单日上涨。韩元兑美元汇率小幅走高。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-10/korean-stocks-gain-after-losing-100-billion-to-political-crisis</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 10 Dec 2024 00:48:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着特朗普推动的反弹开始减弱，加密货币波动性加剧</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-09/bitcoin-btc-wavers-smaller-tokens-sink-as-frothy-crypto-rally-frays</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着当选总统唐纳德·特朗普对加密货币的支持所引发的乐观情绪开始降温，加密货币遭遇了一轮抛售。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-09/bitcoin-btc-wavers-smaller-tokens-sink-as-frothy-crypto-rally-frays</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 09 Dec 2024 23:39:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>交易员权衡中国刺激计划和叙利亚动乱，油价持稳</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-09/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-dec-10</link>
      <description><![CDATA[因投资者权衡明年中国出台更大胆刺激措施的前景，同时市场关注叙利亚政权垮台的后果，油价保持稳定。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-09/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-dec-10</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 09 Dec 2024 23:30:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>亚洲股市因对中国刺激计划的乐观情绪而上涨：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-09/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国高层领导人表示明年将采取更大胆的刺激措施，以重振世界第二大经济体，随后亚洲股市上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-09/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 09 Dec 2024 22:30:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>新日铁为赢得美国工人支持做最后努力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-09/nippon-steel-clarifies-spending-pledge-in-effort-to-save-us-deal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[新日本制铁公司公布了其在美国钢铁公司旗下美国钢厂的支出计划，这是其为争取工人和政界人士支持收购这家匹兹堡钢铁制造商而做出的最后一项努力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-09/nippon-steel-clarifies-spending-pledge-in-effort-to-save-us-deal</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 09 Dec 2024 13:03:40 GMT</pubDate>
